[[File:Spacefoil.jpg|thumb|A spacefoil.]]

A '''spacefoil''' was a proposed upgrade to be utilized on the [[Death Star/Legends|Death Star's]] hull. It would have optimally distributed [[Deflector shield/Legends|deflector shield]] energy, increasing the amount of power that was available for the Death Star's other systems, including its [[Superlaser/Legends|superlaser]].

The spacefoil was immense in size, but otherwise bore a resemblance to the aerodynamic spoilers used on wheeled ground vehicles.

